<div class="container">
    <ul class="nav nav-tabs-custom clearfix">
       
        <li class="active"><a>微店列表</a></li>
        <li><a href="./HotVShop">热门微店管理</a></li>
        <li><a href="./TopShop">主推微店管理</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="queryDiv">
		<img class="queryImg" src="/Images/ic_query.png">
		<div class="tipBox">
			<h5>温馨提示:</h5>
			<ul>
				<li><span>微店是商家店铺在微信端、APP端的一种展示形式，平台设置为主推/热门的微店，在微店列表上会优先进行展示。</span></li>
				<li class="mark-info"><span>注意：即使商家没有开通微店，也可以正常售卖商品。</span></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
    <div class="search-box">
        <form class="custom-inline form-inline">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="label-inline w75" for="">微店名称</label>
                <input class="form-control input-ssm" type="text" id="vshopName">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="label-inline w75" for="">微店类型</label>
                <select class="form-control input-ssm" id="vshopState">
                    <option value="">全部微店</option>
                    <option value="0">普通微店</option>
                    <option value="2">热门微店</option>
                    <option value="1">主推微店</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="label-inline w75" for="">状态</label>
                <select class="form-control input-ssm" id="vshopIsOpen">
                    <option value="">全部状态</option>
                    <option value="true">已开启</option>
                    <option value="false">已关闭</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm clear-v46" onclick="bindSearchBtn()" id="searchButton">搜索</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
    <table id="list" class="table"></table>
</div>
<input type="hidden" id="categoryId" value="" />

<div class="mobile-dialog">
    <iframe name="mobile-iframe" id="mobileshow" frameborder="0" scrolling="auto" src="about:blank"></iframe>
</div>
<div class="cover"></div>



